craterdog.collections.interfaces

Interface Accessible<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element managed by the collection.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bag, ClosedCollection, Collection, Dictionary, List, Map, OpenCollection, OrderedCollection, Queue, Set, SortableCollection, Stack

    public interface Accessible<E>
    This interface defines the methods that must be implemented by each collection whose elements can be iterated over.
    Author:
    Derk Norton
